ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada - Grand Duchy of Luxembourg - Audiovisual Coproduction Treaty
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the AUDIOVISUAL COPRODUCTION TREATY between the Government of Canada and the Government of the GRAND DUCHY OF LUXEMBOURG.
